ops::bit::ShlAssign::shl_assign.doc:
Performs the `<<=` operation.

# Examples

```
let mut x: u8 = 5;
x <<= 1;
assert_eq!(x, 10);

let mut x: u8 = 1;
x <<= 1;
assert_eq!(x, 2);
```

